sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_066_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Get Composite Schedule
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: Central System supports Smart Charging feature profile

    CS->>CP: 1. GetCompositeSchedule.req
    Note left of CS: connectorId: <Configured ConnectorId><br/>duration: <Configured Charging Schedule Duration><br/>chargingRateUnit: <Configured Charging Rate Unit>

    CP-->>CS: 2. GetCompositeSchedule.conf
    Note right of CP: chargingSchedule contains<br/>a hard-coded composite schedule
    Note over CS: Validation: Central System has<br/>retrieved the composite ChargingProfile
